OL,3,CFormer politician Derek Hatton and
OL,4,Cwife deny misconduct in a public office
OL,6,FFormer politician Derek Hatton and his
OL,7,Fwife have denied misconduct in a
OL,8,Fpublic office.
OL,10,FHatton, 77, and Sonjia Hatton, 50,
OL,11,Fappeared at Manchester Crown Court on
OL,12,FFriday.
OL,14,FThe former deputy council leader, who
OL,15,Fwore a navy blue suit with a pocket
OL,16,Fsquare and trainers, entered a not
OL,17,Fguilty plea to a charge of counselling
OL,18,For procuring misconduct in a public
OL,19,Foffice.
