OL,3,CFormer politician Derek Hatton and
OL,4,Cwife deny misconduct in a public office
OL,6,FSonjia Hatton, of Aigburth, Liverpool,
OL,7,Fwho had long blonde hair tied up,
OL,8,Fpleaded not guilty to a charge of
OL,9,Fmisconduct in a public office.
OL,11,FShe is accused of providing her
OL,12,Fhusband with confidential council
OL,13,Finformation over matters of commercial
OL,14,Fand business use.
OL,16,FDerek Hatton, of Mossley Hill,
OL,17,FLiverpool, pleaded not guilty at a
OL,18,Fhearing earlier this year to a charge
OL,19,Fof offering a bribe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
