OL,3,CFormer politician Derek Hatton and
OL,4,Cwife deny misconduct in a public office
OL,6,FThe couple sat next to each other in
OL,7,Fthe well of the court for the hearing
OL,8,Fand Hatton, who was part of Labour's
OL,9,Fmilitant faction in the 1980s, used a
OL,10,Fhearing loop system to listen to
OL,11,Fproceedings.
OL,13,FBoth were bailed to stand trial in
OL,14,FApril 2027 along with former Liverpool
OL,15,Fmayor Joe Anderson, his son David
OL,16,FAnderson and the council's former
OL,17,Fassistant director of highways and
OL,18,Fplanning Andrew Barr.
