OL,3,CFormer politician Derek Hatton and
OL,4,Cwife deny misconduct in a public office
OL,6,FAnderson, 67, of Knotty Ash in
OL,7,FLiverpool, denies bribery, misconduct
OL,8,Fin a public office and conspiracy to
OL,9,Fcommit misconduct in a public office.
OL,11,FHis 38-year-old son, of Wavertree,
OL,12,FLiverpool, denies conspiracy to commit
OL,13,Fmisconduct in a public office and
OL,14,FBarr, 51, of Ainsdale, Merseyside,
OL,15,Fdenies conspiracy to commit misconduct
OL,16,Fin a public office and accepting a
OL,17,Fbribe.
