OL,3,CFormer politician Derek Hatton and
OL,4,Cwife deny misconduct in a public office
OL,6,FThey were charged as part of Operation
OL,7,FAloft, launched by Merseyside Police
OL,8,Fto look into the awarding of
OL,9,Fcommercial and business contracts from
OL,10,Fthe council between 2010 and 2020.
OL,12,FSix other defendants who were charged
OL,13,Fin connection with the investigation
OL,14,Fare due to stand trial in February
OL,15,Fnext year.
